{% schema %}
  {
    
    "name": "Section 3",
    "tag": "section",
    "class": "gps-601462128850764751 gps gpsil",
    "settings": [{"type":"paragraph","content":"Section design by GemPages. [Click here to start design](https://admin.shopify.com/store/w7f2j0-0h/apps/gempages-cro/app/shopify/edit?pageType=GP_STATIC&editorId=601462128766878671&sectionId=601462128850764751)"},{"type":"select","label":"Section Preload","id":"section_preload","options":[{"label":"On","value":"true"},{"label":"Off","value":"false"},{"label":"Off Lazy Script","value":"off_lazy_script"}],"default":"false"},{"type":"text","label":"Checksum","id":"checksum"},{"type":"html","id":"ggCSMdB5uDP_text","label":"ggCSMdB5uDP_text","default":"1.Reverse the \"Hormonal Suffocation\""},{"type":"html","id":"ggkqI3koa6W_text","label":"ggkqI3koa6W_text","default":"<p>During menopause, a rise in DHT-related sensitivity can cause follicles to \"miniaturize.\" They get smaller and smaller until the hair becomes peach fuzz. Radiant Root cleanses the scalp of the specific impurities that allow this miniaturization to happen, giving the follicle room to breathe.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg0Ec4UHS_s_text","label":"gg0Ec4UHS_s_text","default":"2. The \"Dormancy\" vs. \"Death\" Myth"},{"type":"html","id":"ggh1vTawJsJ_text","label":"ggh1vTawJsJ_text","default":"<p>Many women fear their hair follicles are \"dead.\" <strong>Wilhelm Wundt’s</strong> research suggests that tissue is rarely dead it is often just lacking the \"Bodily Substrate\" (nutrients and blood) to function. Rosemary acts as a natural vasodilator to \"wake up\" these dormant roots.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggq0plmZwvW_text","label":"ggq0plmZwvW_text","default":"3. The \"Estrogen-Drop\" Shedding Anchor"},{"type":"html","id":"ggU1wLgJUrS_text","label":"ggU1wLgJUrS_text","default":"<p>As hormones shift, the \"grip\" your scalp has on the hair root loosens. This is why you see \"clumps\" in the drain. Our <strong>Keratin-Bonding mechanism</strong> acts as a structural scaffold, reinforcing the hair at the base so it stays anchored during hormonal fluctuations.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg8n6hnXUGx_text","label":"gg8n6hnXUGx_text","default":"4. High-Science, Low-Effort (The Ogilvy Rule)"},{"type":"html","id":"ggBrq_0CuGA_text","label":"ggBrq_0CuGA_text","default":"<p>Menopause is exhausting enough. You don't need a medical \"program.\" Following <strong>Ogilvy’s</strong> rule of simplicity, we turned a complex scalp treatment into a 3-minute shower routine. It’s the easiest health switch you’ll make this year.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggdkAPeJemo_text","label":"ggdkAPeJemo_text","default":"5. Reclaiming Your Identity"},{"type":"html","id":"ggzbuyoni1h_text","label":"ggzbuyoni1h_text","default":"<p>Hair is more than just \"style\"—it’s how you feel as a woman. By focusing on <strong>Scalp Health first</strong>, we help you move away from the \"thinning\" labels and back toward the version of yourself you recognize in the mirror. Catching your reflection shouldn't be a source of anxiety; it should be a reminder of your resilience.</p>"}],
    "blocks": [{"type": "@app"}],
    "locales": {}
  }
